snippet.title: Mubble – First Trailer
snippet.description:
Mubble is a Minecraft: Java Edition 1.12 mod that lets you discover the Nintendo world through new blocks, items and more!
The first version (1.0) of Mubble will be available this summer in English, French, Spanish.

🔔 Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/MubbleMC

Music: https://youtu.be/6eeIEMOQw4s
